802
01:24:10,690 --> 01:24:12,520
tonight...

803
01:24:12,860 --> 01:24:14,790
Oslo has already won.

804
01:24:18,930 --> 01:24:21,970
I tried calling.
I thought he might be with you.

805
01:24:23,360 --> 01:24:24,390
Oh.

806
01:24:24,420 --> 01:24:27,240
He's okay.
He's uh, he's at a friend's house.

807
01:24:28,270 --> 01:24:30,720
Just didn't bother calling me.

808
01:24:32,100 --> 01:24:33,920
What did you argue about?

809
01:24:35,600 --> 01:24:37,700
