up in Telemark.

814
01:24:54,450 --> 01:24:57,150
And because he consults
all over the place...

815
01:24:57,770 --> 01:24:59,330
it's not too inconvenient.

816
01:25:00,270 --> 01:25:03,180
I saw him the other day,
he didn't mention anything.

817
01:25:06,940 --> 01:25:09,240
Is that really what you want?

818
01:25:10,760 --> 01:25:12,990
I don't know what I want.

819
01:25:19,340 --> 01:25:21,050
I miss you.

820
01:25:27,050 --> 01:25:30,770
<i>My head says 50/50,
but in my heart, 100%.</i>

821
01:25:30,800 --> 01:25:31,980
Thank you for coming.

822
01:25:32,010 --> 01:25:34,590
Mr. Stop?
Mr. Stop, I'm sorry, I um...

823
01:25:35,400 --> 01:25:37,230
I just want to thank you.

824
01:25:37,250 --> 01:25:39,760
I really liked your speech.

825
01:25:39,760 --> 01:25:42,620
I found it very... very moving.

826
01:25:43,910 --> 01:25:45,630
Well, you see, I uh...

827
01:25:46,750 --> 01:25:49,300
I was an orphan myself, so...

828
01:25:50,410 --> 01:25:54,250
Well, it doesn't have to be
a disadvantage, young lady.

829
01:25:54,570 --> 01:25:56,920
It can motivate us, too.

830
01:25:57,450 --> 01:25:58,380
Oh.

831
01:25:59,500 --> 01:26:00,880
Well, yes.

832
01:26:03,260 --> 01:26:07,260
I work in Bergen with-
with young people in a care center

833
01:26:07,290 --> 01:26:09,410
and I know how-
how very busy you are.

834
01:26:09,430 --> 01:26:10,930
But if ever you're
ever in the city...

835
01:26:10,960 --> 01:26:12,540
I started my career in Bergen.

836
01:26:14,280 --> 01:26:16,370
Write to me.
I'll see what I can do.

837
01:26:16,440 --> 01:26:18,020
Yes, I'm so sorry, I know...

838
01:26:18,050 --> 01:26:19,980
