853
01:29:01,610 --> 01:29:03,910
He was with another friend.

854
01:29:07,580 --> 01:29:08,810
Are you okay?

855
01:29:08,840 --> 01:29:10,890
Yes, I-I'm fine now.

856
01:29:14,540 --> 01:29:15,980
Mathias...

857
01:29:16,000 --> 01:29:19,300
<i>Eh, I've got to run now to one
of those boring dinners, but...</i>

858
01:29:19,320 --> 01:29:22,850
I'll call you in the morning
when I'm back. Okay?

859
