World Cup...</i>

873
01:32:02,310 --> 01:32:03,960
<i>has been awarded to...</i>

874
01:32:03,980 --> 01:32:05,590
Two, one...

875
01:32:05,770 --> 01:32:07,370
<i>Oslo.</i>

876
01:32:35,700 --> 01:32:39,140
Oslo! Oslo! Oslo!

877
01:32:41,720 --> 01:32:43,520
Congrats to us all.

878
01:32:58,690 --> 01:33:00,190
Hoo-hoo.

879
