Magnus!

884
01:35:00,090 --> 01:35:01,530
Yeah, sure.

885
01:35:05,500 --> 01:35:06,970
When was this taken?

886
01:35:07,160 --> 01:35:08,460
Two days ago.

887
01:35:08,460 --> 01:35:10,670
<i>- No, no. I'm late...
- I'm sorry, I'm sorry.</i>

888
01:35:10,690 --> 01:35:12,530
<i>to get her to school.
I have to get to work.</i>

889
01:35:12,550 --> 01:35:14,830
