question I need to ask you.</i>

890
01:35:15,040 --> 01:35:16,700
<i>- We have been over this...
- I know.</i>

891
01:35:16,720 --> 01:35:17,650
<i>hundreds of times.</i>

892
01:35:17,700 --> 01:35:19,200
<i>I know we have been over this
