<i>- what day we saw him?
- Sir...</i>

910
01:35:57,310 --> 01:35:59,030
Yes, I want all those files.

911
01:35:59,080 --> 01:36:00,500
Give me your car keys.

912
01:36:00,530 --> 01:36:02,420
- What?
- And your phone.

913
01:36:33,900 --> 01:36:35,160
Yes?

914
01:36:37,510 --> 01:36:40,360
You told me Vetlesen was your
wife's doctor when we spoke.

915
01:36:41,430 --> 01:36:43,740
And that you had no idea
why she'd gone to see him.

916
01:36:44,290 --> 01:36:45,470
Yes.

917
01:36:47,470 --> 01:36:50,810
But you told my colleague
you both went to see him.

918
01:36:51,820 --> 01:36:53,790
She must have misheard me.

919
01:36:55,130 --> 01:36:56,970
She recorded the interview.

920
01:37:02,660 --> 01:37:05,150
Darling, go back inside.
I'll come in in a minute, okay?

921
01:37:08,140 --> 01:37:09,720
Good girl.

922
01:37:11,130 --> 01:37:12,650
She isn't mine.

923
01:37:15,190 --> 01:37:17,800
Birte and I were trying
for another child.

924
01:37:19,740 --> 01:37:21,970
We thought it might
save our marriage.

925
01:37:22,900 --> 01:37:26,120
We had blood tests done in the
clinic for hormone treatment.

926
01:37:26,830 --> 01:37:28,840
And it came out that...

927
01:37:30,050 --> 01:37:31,800
she wasn't mine.

928
01:37:34,470 --> 01:37:36,310
I am infertile.

929
01:37:36,580 --> 01:37:38,450
Always been infertile.

930
01:37:40,640 --> 01:37:42,320
Can't have children.

931
01:37:43,780 --> 01:37:45,490
But she is mine.

932
01:37:45,810 --> 01:37:47,630
Do you understand?

933
01:37:48,480 --> 01:37:50,350
How can I not love her?

934
01:37:54,070 --> 01:37:57,300
But you didn't see Vetlesen
the day you found out?

935
01:38:02,530 --> 01:38:05,930
No, we saw some
hormone specialist.

936
01:38:06,420 --> 01:38:08,530
Visiting consultant.

937
01:38:14,450 --> 01:38:16,460
Do you know his name?

938
01:38:24,800 --> 01:38:26,150
Yes?

939
01:38:29,350 --> 01:38:30,820
Just a second.

940
01:38:32,490 --> 01:38:33,670
Damn it.

941
01:38:35,900 --> 01:38:38,090
I said I'm coming.

942
01:38:45,030 --> 01:38:46,660
You never called.

943
01:38:48,440 --> 01:38:50,020
Is Oleg back?

944
01:38:50,410 --> 01:38:53,170
What? Oleg?
He-he's at school.

945
01:38:55,220 --> 01:38:57,140
And Harry?

946
01:38:57,950 --> 01:38:59,330
Is Harry here?

947
01:39:01,470 --> 01:39:02,800
No.

948
01:39:03,030 --> 01:39:04,080
No?

949
01:39:06,750 --> 01:39:10,090
